IN RE PRISCILLA A.
S241995
Supreme Court of California
July 12, 2017
The petition for review is granted. Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition of a related issue in In re R.T., S226416 (see Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512 (d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court.
